<p>
<lb n="1"/>Āmallebō
<lb n="2" break="no"/>yuni koḍku pōtanabō
<lb n="3" break="no"/>yuṁḍu tama taṁḍri guḍi
<lb n="4" break="no"/>vāḍa mallebōyuniki ta 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ma talli Eṟakāsāniki dharmma
<lb n="6" break="no"/>vugānu śakava<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>ṣaṁbulu
<lb n="7"/>1159 Agunēṁṭi śrāhini
<lb n="8"/>Ūri paḍmaṭaṁ jēyiṁccina
<lb n="9"/>Iṭṭikanuyini kalugāḍini
<lb n="10"/>Ā gāḍiki nīḍlettivāriki jī
<lb n="11" break="no"/>tānakani guḍivāḍa paḍmaṭa
<lb n="12"/>vidarbhbha Uttaramu kuṁṭa cē
<lb n="13" break="no"/>nu kha 1 <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> yī dharmmuvu Ā
<lb n="14" break="no"/>caṁdrārkkamu Eḍapaku
<lb n="15" break="no"/>ṁḍā nevverainā naḍapina vā
<lb n="16" break="no"/>ru mammēlivāru <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
</p>

